Let me go. Master!

59
00:03:42,119 --> 00:03:43,520
What did I do wrong?

60
00:03:44,080 --> 00:03:45,880
It was Chong Zi who killed Zhuo Yunji

61
00:03:46,119 --> 00:03:47,199
and hurt Yue Qiao.

62
