about the common people,

78
00:04:28,719 --> 00:04:29,759
what's the use?

79
00:04:30,159 --> 00:04:31,120
Over the years,

80
00:04:31,879 --> 00:04:33,439
I have been practicing Mirror Heart Skill,

81
00:04:34,120 --> 00:04:35,279
just to get rid of the evil breath

82
